headline: Nutri-Grain Rolls Out the Nutri-Grain Lounge to Give Teachers the Break They Deserve
summary: Nutri‑Grain® is setting a new standard for how teachers are appreciated this school year. For decades, students have brought their teachers apples. A nice gesture, sure — but at this point, one that feels more symbolic than supportive. This year, Nutri-Grain gives that tired tradition a well-earned upgrade with the Nutri-Grain Lounge: a fully decked-out teacher's lounge on wheels, designed to give teachers a moment to pause, recharge, and reset amid the back-to-school frenzy.
